			<h3>About Me</h3>
			<p>
				I'm a transplant from Boston in San Diego, where I manage a software QA engineering team for a late-stage startup.
			</p>
			<p>
				I love connecting with new people and am always looking for opportunities to grow. To stay up to date on my thoughts and endeavors, check out my blog, <a href="https://the-residual.com">The Residual</a>.
