			<h3>Where I've Been</h3>
			<p>
				I graduated from Amherst College in May 2019 with degrees in Computer Science and Philosophy. Along the way, I took courses in algorithms, data structures, computer systems, and machine learning, among others. I was also Co-Founder and CTO of <a href="https://www.rateourcourses.com" target="_blank">RateOurCourses.com</a>, a course and professor review website for Amherst students.
			</p>
			<p>
